EEGCoordinateSystemDescription: Orientation ALS (x-anterior, y-left, z-superior). Montage is international 10-10 system. Coordinates lay in the range [-1,1]. The origin is between LPA and RPA, the X-axis goes towards te nasion, the Y-axis goes approximately towards LPA, orthogonal to X, and the Z-axis goes approximately towards the vertex, orthogonal to X and Y.
